                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4">Best Practices</h3>
                    <ul class="space-y-2" style="list-style: disc; padding-left: 1.5rem;">
                        <li><strong>Use clear labels:</strong> Button text should clearly describe the action</li>
                        <li><strong>Provide tooltips:</strong> Use Tooltip parameter for icon-only buttons</li>
                        <li><strong>Indicate loading:</strong> Always show loading state during async operations</li>
